TO AUTOMATE SELECTING ALL CHECKBOXES IN A PAGE DOM AND SAVE THEM ON CLICK OF THE SAVE BUTTON IN JAVASCRIPT, YOU CAN FOLLOW THESE STEPS:

1. FIRST, MAKE SURE EACH CHECKBOX HAS A UNIQUE OR COMMON CLASS NAME OR ID FOR EASIER SELECTION.
2. USE JQUERY OR PURE JS TO SELECT ALL CHECKBOXES AND SET THEM TO CHECKED.
3. ADD AN EVENT LISTENER TO THE SAVE BUTTON TO TRIGGER THE CHECKBOX SELECTION.

HERE IS AN EXAMPLE USING PURE JS:

```HTML
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Auto Select Checkboxes</title>
</head>
<body>
    <input type="checkbox" class="auto-select"> Checkbox 1
    <input type="checkbox" class="auto-select"> Checkbox 2
    <button id="saveButton">Save</button>

    <script>
        // SELECT ALL CHECKBOXES WITH THE CLASS 'AUTO-SELECT' AND CHECK THEM
        const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.auto-select');
        checkboxes.forEach(checkbox => checkbox.checked = true);

        // ADD AN EVENT LISTENER TO THE SAVE BUTTON
        document.getElementById('saveButton').addEventListener('click', function() {
            // HERE YOU CAN ALSO HANDLE THE SAVING LOGIC, LIKE SENDING DATA TO SERVER
            console.log('Checkboxes have been saved.');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

IF YOU WANT TO AUTOMATICALLY CHECK THE BOXES WHEN THE DOCUMENT LOADS, YOU CAN MOVE THE CHECKBOX SELECTION CODE OUT OF THE SAVE BUTTON CLICK HANDLER:

```HTML
<script>
    // SELECT ALL CHECKBOXES WITH THE CLASS 'AUTO-SELECT' AND CHECK THEM ON DOCUMENT LOAD
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
        const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.auto-select');
        checkboxes.forEach(checkbox => checkbox.checked = true);
    });

    // ADD AN EVENT LISTENER TO THE SAVE BUTTON
    document.getElementById('saveButton').addEventListener('click', function() {
        // HERE YOU CAN ALSO HANDLE THE SAVING LOGIC, LIKE SENDING DATA TO SERVER
        console.log('Checkboxes have been saved.');
    });
</script>
```

THIS WAY, THE CHECKBOXES WILL BE AUTOMATICALLY SELECTED AS SOON AS THE PAGE LOADS, AND YOU CAN STILL MANUALLY SAVE THEM BY CLICKING THE SAVE BUTTON.

